{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3b471c1ce2","title":"张春桥姚文元视察上海第八印染厂时的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f0b1027944","index":0,"year":1967,"month":10,"day":4,"articleId":"3b471c1ce2","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"大联合","id":"18bf6a78fe","type":"主题"},{"name":"刘少奇","id":"3aaab89c2a","type":"人物"},{"name":"暴力和武斗","id":"3bff1d2fc6","type":"主题"},{"name":"张春桥","id":"471a503675","type":"人物"},{"name":"王洪文","id":"8e2c446eb1","type":"人物"},{"name":"姚文元","id":"92a8a42842","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"yaowenyuan","name":"姚文元文录","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"姚文元","files":"/books/姚文元文录.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"zhangchunqiao","name":"春桥文录","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张春桥","files":"/books/zhangchunqiao.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"45f848c5df","name":"姚文元"},{"id":"fae13ac6b9","name":"张春桥"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"485f10c292","type":"title","text":"张春桥姚文元视察上海第八印染厂时的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ed42bec3cd","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：大家节日过得好吗？（答：过得好。）","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"353545d4ea","type":"paragraph","text":"张：听说你们厂里毛著学习班办得很好，你们是不是找几个人来谈谈，开个座谈会好吗？（好啊）","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9b4c79f798","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你们现在分几派？（答：一派。）","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ef84fc420b","type":"paragraph","text":"张：武斗过没有？（没有，我们黄浦区都比较好，没发生武斗。）","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aaa0987342","type":"paragraph","text":"张：黄浦区没发生过武斗？铁道学院可发生武斗吗？（他们是学校，我们是工厂。）","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"498d4fec33","type":"paragraph","text":"张：武斗也没什么，斗一斗也好嘛！（在谈到北上返沪兵团时。）","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9ec426a549","type":"paragraph","text":"姚文元笑着说：噢！对，是那个××司令，对吧？","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1235b4b80c","type":"paragraph","text":"张：后来我找王洪文，和他谈了许多，当时他们两人都有小山头，我说你们两个党员都不能团结起来，怎么能行呢？都是工总司的嘛。你们化工厂武斗起来很厉害，（是的，在文攻武卫的时候，我们想造燃烧弹，催泪弹，什么都想搞。）（汇报略）","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c856b54729","type":"paragraph","text":"张：学习毛主席著作要靠积极分子，发动群众来学习，现在要抓紧这两天的学习，你们这样轻视劳动，还想当干部，高人一等，你们想想，吃的、穿的还不都是工人农民劳动创造的，工人农民最光荣，劳动最光荣。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"478476733f","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：这个问题要放在文化革命运动中解决，干部应该能上能下。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"86f8f15bec","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你们也是革委会干部，你们也要能上能下，劳动，要多接近群众，这个问题很重要，不然再隔几年，你们也会要犯错误，当然不一定是走资派，这不是小节问题，是立场问题，希望你们不要把矛盾上交，这种人踢出去人家也不要的，就放在车间里劳动吧，等以后再处理么（众：我们在斗这个走资派时，他还拿刘少奇的话跟我们辩论。）这样很好么，这样隔一段时期，就拿几个问题跟他辩一辩，他们就会有事做了，就不会只管生产了。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"75ff6dfe87","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：资产阶级思想核心，修正主义核心就是私。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"884252259a","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你们厂造反造得早，你们是否可以探索斗、批、改，我也没有经验，你们自己揭，总结一套经验。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}},"yaowenyuan":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"07123a1d35","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你们也是革委会干部，你们也要能上能下，劳动，要多接近群众，这个问题很重要，不然再隔几年，你们也会要犯错误，当然不一定是走资派，这不是小节问题，是立场问题，希望你们不要把矛盾上交，这种人踢出去人家也不要的，就放在车间里劳动吧，等以后再处理么（众：我们在斗这个走资派时，他还拿刘少奇的话跟我们辩论。）这样很好么，这样隔一段时期，就拿几个问题跟他辩一辩，他们就会有事做了，就不会只管生产了。","index":12,"publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0b7b31b67d","type":"title","text":"张春桥姚文元视察上海第八印染厂时的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1b67bb73d7","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：资产阶级思想核心，修正主义核心就是私。","index":13,"publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1c2631018a","type":"paragraph","text":"张：武斗过没有？（没有，我们黄浦区都比较好，没发生武斗。）","index":4,"publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"33021458d6","type":"paragraph","text":"张：黄浦区没发生过武斗？铁道学院可发生武斗吗？（他们是学校，我们是工厂。）","index":5,"publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"46920a79d4","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你们厂造反造得早，你们是否可以探索斗、批、改，我也没有经验，你们自己揭，总结一套经验。","index":14,"publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"49eeea8a92","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：这个问题要放在文化革命运动中解决，干部应该能上能下。","index":11,"publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"61b14100f7","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：大家节日过得好吗？（答：过得好。）","index":1,"publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"96d684df90","type":"paragraph","text":"张：你们现在分几派？（答：一派。）","index":3,"publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9a9b6c7747","type":"paragraph","text":"姚文元笑着说：噢！对，是那个××司令，对吧？","index":7,"publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9c3054229d","type":"paragraph","text":"张：武斗也没什么，斗一斗也好嘛！（在谈到北上返沪兵团时。）","index":6,"publicationId":"yaowenyuan","articleId":"3b471c1ce2","pu